highlights.text: “The Glen - Levi Heron Edit” by Levi Heron has been on Viral Songs Sweden the longest, at 122 days straight.
“What a Difference a Day Makes (from the Netflix Limited Series "Black Rabbit")” by RAYE is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Sweden at #89.
Mio Johansson has the most spots on Viral Songs Sweden. “Vetlösa hardtekk - Remix” is the highest at #8.
“Montagem Supersonic” by KHAOS and Jmilton is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Sweden, up 13 spots at #60.
